.1</span> 標題：卡布（qab）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： קַב</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： qav)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:25\">2KI 6:25</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:25\">2KI 6:25</a> ：這裡<em>qav</em> （「卡布」）的四分之一約等於半升。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 譯為“half a pound”（「半磅」）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 採用容器來計量，譯為“a small bowl”（「一小碗」）。在大多數情況下，採用容器都是一個很好的解決方案。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
